entry.summary:
This lets you do so many cool things, even joining across disparate services: select aws.name aws_user_name, slack.id as slack_user_id, slack.display_name as slack_name from aws_iam_user as aws, slack_user as slack where aws.name = slack.email;
+--------------------------+---------------+------------+ | aws_user_name | slack_user_id | slack_name | +--------------------------+---------------+------------+ | dwight@dundermifflin.com | U2EMB8HLP | dwight | | jim@dundermifflin.com | U02HE4Z7E | jim | +--------------------------+---------------+------------+
Useful for compliance, security, ops, and cost management. Discuss on Changelog News

